WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
<b>Origami</b> is the art of turning paper into creative shapes.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
With a few simple folds, a paper airplane begins to take shape.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Each line must be made with care and precision.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
The result is an elegant and easy-to-make model.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Origami develops patience and creativity.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Discover more models on <b>Shop Origami</b>.